Package: neuromesh
Type: Package
Title: Neuroimaging Mesh Visualization for scimesh
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tim", "Schaefer", email = "ts+code@rcmd.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A neuroimaging layer on top of the scimesh software
    renderer. Provides FreeSurfer-aware functions for loading brain
    surface meshes, mapping morphometry data to vertex colours via
    standard colormaps, cortex masking, anatomical camera views
    (lateral, medial, dorsal, ventral, anterior, posterior), and
    multi-view figure composition with colour bars.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/dfsp-spirit/neuromesh
BugReports: https://github.com/dfsp-spirit/neuromesh/issues
Imports:
    scimesh,
    freesurferformats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    png,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
SystemRequirements: none
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: no
